              "message": "`OS-02` still says the single-vs-split grounding ref type decision is deferred to Phase 2, but the Phase 2 artifacts have already closed that choice on a shared `DecisionGroundRef` (`domain-types.json` also makes `AdrDecisionCommon` use `Option<DecisionGroundRef>`). The plan set is internally inconsistent about whether this architecture decision is still open.",
