            {
              "message": "IN-06 and AC-08 describe the fail-closed empty-placeholder behavior as belonging to `CN-04`, but `CN-04` is the domain/infrastructure placement constraint; the actual fail-closed constraint is `CN-01`. The impl plan and infrastructure catalogue already use `CN-01` for this behavior, so the spec/rendered spec currently contain a broken cross-reference that can send implementation and coverage review to the wrong constraint.",
