              "message": "`domain-types.md` renders `DecisionGroundRef` with action `—`, while the scoped JSON SSoT declares `DecisionGroundRef.action` as `add`. That is a cross-artifact contradiction in the planning view and can mislead readers about whether the new value object is actually part of the planned domain changes.",
